Enter advanced configuration options.

Select how frequently the SD Elements and RTC projects are synchronized. You can choose from the following options. The more frequently you run synchronization, the greater the performance impact on both the SD Elements and RTC servers. This is generally only a concern for large organizations running many synchronizations at once.
